---
import { ADDRESS, EMAIL, PHONE, SOCIAL_MEDIA } from '@/config/constants'
---

<footer class="border-neutral/20 bg-primary border-t">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-12 flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="w-[300px]">
        <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/logo-white.png" alt="Égida Jurídica" class="w-50 h-15 object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex w-full items-start justify-end gap-24">
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-white">Empresa</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="/areas" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Area práctica</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/nosotros" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Nosotros</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/contacto" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Contacto</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-white">Áreas de práctica</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="/areas" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Derecho empresarial</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/areas" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Derecho civil</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-white">Servicios</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="/contacto" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Derecho laboral</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/contacto" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Derecho tributario</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/contacto" class="text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Derecho penal</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-neutral/20 mb-8" />

    <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-4 max-w-md text-white/90">
          Égida Jurídica, antes conocida como Aguirre Legal Group, fundado en 2017 por abogados
          experimentados del sector privado, es una firma especializada en derecho corporativo,
          cumplimiento normativo y asesoría en inversiones. Hemos construido nuestra reputación a
          través de referencias y recomendaciones de clientes satisfechos.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span>{PHONE}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span>{EMAIL}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"
              ></path>
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>{ADDRESS}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href={SOCIAL_MEDIA.FACEBOOK}
          target="_blank"
          class="hover:text-primary flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center bg-white/10 transition-colors hover:bg-white/15"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 640 640"
            class="h-5 w-5 text-white"
            fill="#FFF"
            ><path
              d="M576 320C576 178.6 461.4 64 320 64C178.6 64 64 178.6 64 320C64 440 146.7 540.8 258.2 568.5L258.2 398.2L205.4 398.2L205.4 320L258.2 320L258.2 286.3C258.2 199.2 297.6 158.8 383.2 158.8C399.4 158.8 427.4 162 438.9 165.2L438.9 236C432.9 235.4 422.4 235 409.3 235C367.3 235 351.1 250.9 351.1 292.2L351.1 320L434.7 320L420.3 398.2L351 398.2L351 574.1C477.8 558.8 576 450.9 576 320z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-neutral/20 my-8" />

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-white/80 sm:flex-row">
      <p>Copyright © 2025 Égida Jurídica</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <button
          class="flex items-center text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-white"
          onclick="window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' })"
        >
          Volver arriba
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
